creator: Fabulessly Frugal
descriptionHtml:
Save money like never before! Discover Amazon discounts, trending online deals & coupons. Shop smart & save time! Custom price alerts mean you’ll never miss a deal!

• Alerts:
Looking to save money on household essentials? Choose from hundreds of products, set an alert for what you need, and we’ll send you a notification when we find a deal on the products that matter most to you!

• Price Comparisons:
Have you found the perfect product, but don’t know if you’re getting the best price on that product? Check out our Price Comparisons, we researched more than 100 products and compared the prices from 6 top national retailers so you know where to get the best price!

• Deals & Filter:
Browse live deals as they are posted on the site. Use our industry-leading filter, to narrow down your options to quickly find that perfect gift.

• Price Points:
Remember that time you stocked up on that household item at the grocery store, and you thought you were getting a fantastic deal, only to find out you could have had it delivered to your doorstep for even less? Our Price Point guide ensures that never happens again. We’ve uncovered all the products, sizes, and pricing for top brands for everyday household products. You will ALWAYS know when you have found a stock up price!
descriptionShort: Give us your shopping burden! Set your alerts, sit back, and save!
